	<div class="pb-md-5">
		<p>Our promise to you is that we will make sure to deliver any order placed before Thursday every on Friday and any order placed by Friday will be delivered on Saturday.
			Unfortunately we do not deliver any orders outside of these specified days. Reason being we are reliant on our farmers to deliver freshly harvest every week therefore orders are delivered once a week.
			We currently only serve the Johannesburg metro area with the prospect widening our coverage areas depending on our suppliers. If you know of farmers society or you a potential farmer looking to supply 
			us, please go to <a href="contact.aspx">Contact page</a> for contact details and we will respond soonest. The farmers we have supplying us the easily we will spread to other areas.
		</p>
		<p>We are a very pro-environment group as such all orders are packaged in reusable bags or crates depending on the size of the order. For every order placed delivery day will be communicated to via mail/sms. 
			Please note that the first reusable bag will be on us. For following orders our delivery guys will be given strict instrcutions that they must get the bag first before handing over your order. In event the bag is not available 
			you will have to provide means for our guys to unload your order.
		</p>
